BMW, a German multinational company founded in 1916, is a renowned luxury automaker celebrated for its premium vehicles, innovative engineering, and driving dynamics. From iconic models like the 3 Series and 5 Series to the performance-oriented M lineup, BMW's cars embody a blend of luxury, sportiness, and cutting-edge technology. Beyond automobiles, BMW Group encompasses brands such as Mini and Rolls-Royce, with a commitment to sustainability reflected in electric 
offerings like the i3 and iX. With a rich history of craftsmanship and a
focus on the future of mobility, BMW continues to be a symbol of automotive
excellence, captivating enthusiasts worldwide.